title: fyoung55
author: fyoung55
content: I want to get my s17 back up to 100%.  I had 2 boards throw pic errors, so I'd like to replace them.  What do you have?

comments.author: betosworld
comments.body: We have 1000s of 17 series miners here in our TX warehouse. We are the original owners and the facility is used to comprehensively refurbish/repair the defective Bitmain solder they were manufactured with.Let me know if you still need 17 series parts.
